name: ‚ùñ Component navigation
description:
These components are mainly for the convenience of UI/UX designers who are building component libraries to do a navigation.

Designer can replace the instance icon inside


You can add new components to Main Component according to your needs, or you can change the name of the component and put it in the "Component" series


At the same time, for the convenience of Chinese users, I added a Chinese component to the name of the cell. Just find the Chinese naming layer of the Main Component and make it displayable, and you can see all the Chinese names in the Navigation Frame, and vice versa, Close to hide Chinese name
